title: Chouritsu!! Momonoki Koukou
sinopse:
Marino Mori's secret is... she's an ESPer!! However she is unable to control her powers very well... and tries to keep it a secret from everyone around her. Just when she thought she could "enjoy a normal high school life," her classmate Shiro accidentally sees her using her mysterious powers?!

(Source: An Endless Story)
